      "raw_text": "Much new work is planned for the\ncoming season along the line of the\nSpokane Falls 4 Northern railroad.\nTwo work trains and a full crew OF\nmen were started out this morning\nand they will be sent along the line\nstrengthening the roadbed in many\nplaces where It has been weakened\nduring the recent stormy weather.\n\n\nAs soon as the season Is opened\nup and the frost out of the ground\nextensive work will be started to\nstraighten curves and provide cut\noffs"
